
Add the following lines to the user generated configurations section of batocera.conf file if your mame vector games don't look good.  This enables the hlsl shaders for a much improved appearance.
 


mame.core=mame
mame.emulator=mame
mame.bezel=thebezelproject
mame.customcfg=1
vectrex.bezel=thebezelproject
mame["armora.zip"].bgfxshaders=hlsl
mame["armora.zip"].video=bgfx
mame["astdelux.zip"].bgfxshaders=hlsl
mame["astdelux.zip"].video=bgfx
mame["asteroid.zip"].bgfxshaders=hlsl
mame["asteroid.zip"].video=bgfx
